sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API
    participant Orchestrator
    participant Agents
    participant LLM
    participant Workspace

    User->>Frontend: Submit project requirements
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/v1/projects
    API->>Orchestrator: Create project instance
    Orchestrator->>Workspace: Create project directory
    Orchestrator->>Agents: Initialize PlannerAgent

    Agents->>LLM: Clarify requirements (Gemini)
    LLM-->>Agents: Clarification response
    Agents->>Agents: Retrieve similar experiences
    Agents->>LLM: Generate execution plan (Gemini)
    LLM-->>Agents: Task breakdown

    Agents-->>Orchestrator: Planning complete
    Orchestrator-->>API: Project created
    API-->>Frontend: ProjectResponse
    Frontend-->>User: Display project dashboard